# ...but keep the directory placeholders tracked (the bare `results/` rule above
# would otherwise swallow backtest/results/.gitkeep).
!backtest/ticks/
!backtest/results/
!backtest/ticks/.gitkeep
!backtest/results/.gitkeep
# Offline-simulator RUN OUTPUT (sim/reports/<run-id>/...) is local, like run/ — never committed.
sim/
# Part 1A offline-simulator PER-DAY cache (XAUUSD_YYYY-MM-DD.parquet) + manifest are
# INTENTIONALLY committable: the gate must be reproducible from the committed cache
# (run `fetchticks` on the VPS, then commit backtest/ticks/*.parquet + manifest.json).
# If a month of ticks is too large for git, switch these paths to git-lfs.
